opensalestax-sylius — dual license declaration
==============================================

This software is distributed under your choice of either:

* Apache License, Version 2.0 (Apache-2.0)
  — see ``LICENSE-APACHE.txt``, OR
* GNU General Public License, version 2 or later
  (GPL-2.0-or-later) — see ``LICENSE-GPL.txt``.

SPDX expression: ``Apache-2.0 OR GPL-2.0-or-later``.

Recipient picks. Most consumers — including merchants embedding
the bundle in their own Sylius deployment — will find Apache-2.0
sufficient. The GPL-2.0-or-later option exists to keep the dual-
license footprint consistent across the broader OpenSalesTax
portfolio (the WooCommerce connector ships the same dual; the
Odoo connector ships LGPL-3.0-or-later OR AGPL-3.0-or-later for
analogous cross-ecosystem reasons).

Contributors agree their contributions are licensed under both
options (see ``CONTRIBUTING.md``).

